#include <stdio.h>
#include <iostream>
#include <string>

using namespace std;

int main()
{
    int n, k=1, totdays, days, year, leap, mon=0;
    string inp, month;
    int numofdays[][12] = { {0,31,59,90,120,151,181,212,243,273,304,334},
                     {0,31,60,91,121,152,182,213,244,274,305,335} };

    cin>>n;
    while(n--)
    {
        cin>>inp;
        days = (((inp[0] - '0') * 10) + ((inp[1] - '0') * 1));
        month = "";
        month = month + inp[3] + inp[4] + inp[5];
        year = ((inp[7] - '0') * 1000) + ((inp[8] - '0') * 100) + ((inp[9] - '0') * 10) + ((inp[10] - '0') * 1);
         leap=0;
          if(year%25==0)
          {
               if(year%16==0)
                    leap=1;
               else
                    leap=0;
          }
          else if(year%4==0)
               leap=1;
          else
               leap=0;

        if (month == "JAN")
        mon = 0;
        else
        if (month == "FEB")
        mon = 1;
        else
        if (month == "MAR")
        mon = 2;
        else
        if (month == "APR")
        mon = 3;
        else
        if (month == "MAY")
        mon = 4;
        else
        if (month == "JUN")
        mon = 5;
        else
        if (month == "JUL")
        mon = 6;
        else
        if (month == "AUG")
        mon = 7;
        else
        if (month == "SEP")
        mon = 8;
        else
        if (month == "OCT")
        mon = 9;
        else
        if (month == "NOV")
        mon = 10;
        else
        if (month == "DEC")
        mon = 11;
        totdays = days + numofdays[leap][mon];
        if (totdays <= 300)
        {
            cout<<"Case "<<k++<<": "<<totdays<<" "<<"Hundreds\n" ;
        }
        else
        if (totdays <= 360)
        {
            cout<<"Case "<<k++<<": "<<(totdays - 300)<<" "<<"Tens\n" ;
        }
        else
        {
            cout<<"Case "<<k++<<": "<<(totdays - 360)<<" "<<"Ones\n" ;
        }

    }

    return 0;
}
